[
  {
    "id": 5949,
    "number": 1,
    "key": "87:1",
    "textAr": "سَبِّحِ ٱسْمَ رَبِّكَ ٱلْأَعْلَى",
    "textEn": "Exalt the name of your Lord, the Most High,",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 591,
    "hizb": 60
  },
  {
    "id": 5950,
    "number": 2,
    "key": "87:2",
    "textAr": "ٱلَّذِى خَلَقَ فَسَوَّىٰ",
    "textEn": "Who created and proportioned",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 591,
    "hizb": 60
  },
  {
    "id": 5951,
    "number": 3,
    "key": "87:3",
    "textAr": "وَٱلَّذِى قَدَّرَ فَهَدَىٰ",
    "textEn": "And who destined and [then] guided",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 591,
    "hizb": 60
  },
  {
    "id": 5952,
    "number": 4,
    "key": "87:4",
    "textAr": "وَٱلَّذِىٓ أَخْرَجَ ٱلْمَرْعَىٰ",
    "textEn": "And who brings out the pasture",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 591,
    "hizb": 60
  },
  {
    "id": 5953,
    "number": 5,
    "key": "87:5",
    "textAr": "فَجَعَلَهُۥ غُثَآءً أَحْوَىٰ",
    "textEn": "And [then] makes it black stubble.",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 591,
    "hizb": 60
  },
  {
    "id": 5954,
    "number": 6,
    "key": "87:6",
    "textAr": "سَنُقْرِئُكَ فَلَا تَنسَىٰٓ",
    "textEn": "We will make you recite, [O Muḥammad], and you will not forget,",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 591,
    "hizb": 60
  },
  {
    "id": 5955,
    "number": 7,
    "key": "87:7",
    "textAr": "إِلَّا مَا شَآءَ ٱللَّهُ ۚ إِنَّهُۥ يَعْلَمُ ٱلْجَهْرَ وَمَا يَخْفَىٰ",
    "textEn": "Except what Allāh should will. Indeed, He knows what is declared and what is hidden.",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 591,
    "hizb": 60
  },
  {
    "id": 5956,
    "number": 8,
    "key": "87:8",
    "textAr": "وَنُيَسِّرُكَ لِلْيُسْرَىٰ",
    "textEn": "And We will ease you toward ease.",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 591,
    "hizb": 60
  },
  {
    "id": 5957,
    "number": 9,
    "key": "87:9",
    "textAr": "فَذَكِّرْ إِن نَّفَعَتِ ٱلذِّكْرَىٰ",
    "textEn": "So remind, if the reminder should benefit;",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 591,
    "hizb": 60
  },
  {
    "id": 5958,
    "number": 10,
    "key": "87:10",
    "textAr": "سَيَذَّكَّرُ مَن يَخْشَىٰ",
    "textEn": "He who fears [Allāh] will be reminded.",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 591,
    "hizb": 60
  },
  {
    "id": 5959,
    "number": 11,
    "key": "87:11",
    "textAr": "وَيَتَجَنَّبُهَا ٱلْأَشْقَى",
    "textEn": "But the wretched one will avoid it",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 591,
    "hizb": 60
  },
  {
    "id": 5960,
    "number": 12,
    "key": "87:12",
    "textAr": "ٱلَّذِى يَصْلَى ٱلنَّارَ ٱلْكُبْرَىٰ",
    "textEn": "[He] who will [enter and] burn in the greatest Fire,",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 591,
    "hizb": 60
  },
  {
    "id": 5961,
    "number": 13,
    "key": "87:13",
    "textAr": "ثُمَّ لَا يَمُوتُ فِيهَا وَلَا يَحْيَىٰ",
    "textEn": "Neither dying therein nor living.",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 591,
    "hizb": 60
  },
  {
    "id": 5962,
    "number": 14,
    "key": "87:14",
    "textAr": "قَدْ أَفْلَحَ مَن تَزَكَّىٰ",
    "textEn": "He has certainly succeeded who purifies himself",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 591,
    "hizb": 60
  },
  {
    "id": 5963,
    "number": 15,
    "key": "87:15",
    "textAr": "وَذَكَرَ ٱسْمَ رَبِّهِۦ فَصَلَّىٰ",
    "textEn": "And mentions the name of his Lord and prays.",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 591,
    "hizb": 60
  },
  {
    "id": 5964,
    "number": 16,
    "key": "87:16",
    "textAr": "بَلْ تُؤْثِرُونَ ٱلْحَيَوٰةَ ٱلدُّنْيَا",
    "textEn": "But you prefer the worldly life,",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 592,
    "hizb": 60
  },
  {
    "id": 5965,
    "number": 17,
    "key": "87:17",
    "textAr": "وَٱلْـَٔاخِرَةُ خَيْرٌ وَأَبْقَىٰٓ",
    "textEn": "While the Hereafter is better and more enduring.",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 592,
    "hizb": 60
  },
  {
    "id": 5966,
    "number": 18,
    "key": "87:18",
    "textAr": "إِنَّ هَـٰذَا لَفِى ٱلصُّحُفِ ٱلْأُولَىٰ",
    "textEn": "Indeed, this is in the former scriptures,",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 592,
    "hizb": 60
  },
  {
    "id": 5967,
    "number": 19,
    "key": "87:19",
    "textAr": "صُحُفِ إِبْرَٰهِيمَ وَمُوسَىٰ",
    "textEn": "The scriptures of Abraham and Moses.",
    "juz": 30,
    "page": 592,
    "hizb": 60
  }
]